Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:48.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at Dublith, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:51.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Were you dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.64,0:01:53.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A dream about {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:03.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:04.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:08.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the Master isn't home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:23.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.03,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.62,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to shrink...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:31.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hi... It's me, Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:37.71,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You've {\i1}really{\i0\fscx30} {\r} gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:42.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've been patted on the head since I became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:46.14,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi, the Elric runts are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.76,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.32,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.34,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling too bad today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:54.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she was lying down because she wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Has her body not healed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.00,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're one idiot of a disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.40,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this I hear about you becoming a dog of the military?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:22.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Master! W-Well... about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:26.97,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Look at how much you've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.14,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed much either, Mast-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.71,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You've slacked on your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:38.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:41.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:44.70,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that! I'm out of bed like this because I heard you guys were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.20,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:54.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about me, Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:01.35,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.58,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:10.47,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,We met an alchemist in Central who knew a lot about the stone, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.71,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I think his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,...Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:29.99,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So he's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.04,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He's our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.69,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So the one who left a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:46.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault Mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.03,0:04:48.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:57.40,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What are you doing up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al said he needed to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.78,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were taking care of Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.60,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:38.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,When's he coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:47.13,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle tickle tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle tickle tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.87,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and finish your meal, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:05:59.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:02.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:30.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So... did Dad say anything about the stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:35.30,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,He looked happy, saying something about his wish from long ago will finally be coming true soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.41,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:43.63,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.16,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to eat, Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:54.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I ate too much on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Al, tell them about how we witnessed childbirth over at Rush Valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Master, we helped a baby being born!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:07.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, that doesn't count as "helping".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that people are born because everyone in the family works together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:15.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,the mother risks her life, and because the person receives so many blessings from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:16.81,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.05,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you two were given life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.29,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud that you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:33.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Master hasn't changed at all, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:39.31,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't changed at all since we first met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:52.89,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.91,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Bring over some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.24,Default,Man3,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.42,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The levee's going to break! Run for high ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.24,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.87,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This should last for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.87,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.55,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,A passing housewife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please be our master, old lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't catch exactly what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mind repeating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:10.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,C-Correction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please be our master, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.19,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.38,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.84,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't take students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:17.66,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we're in the middle of a trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please, accept us as your students!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.72,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.18,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have permission from your parents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.04,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is... those boys don't have any parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:34.03,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so soft when it comes to things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.06,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Survive on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.23,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.12,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the preliminary round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.43,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you pass, we'll get to the real training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:54.24,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not allowed to use alchemy during this preliminary round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:55.49,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.35,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,"One is All, All is One."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:01.12,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Find the answer to that within a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.79,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, I'm sending you back to Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.67,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.99,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.13,0:10:23.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sleep in a bed, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:35.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this is alchemy training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.46,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if those kids are all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.02,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They say there's no substitute for real-life experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:11:01.22,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That is the best way to pound the courage portion of alchemy into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:06.77,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't learn anything from this,\Nit just means that's the extent of their talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:09.06,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll have to give up learning from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:16.07,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm worried about is the safety of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:21.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was thrown out to Mt. Briggs in the middle of winter for a month during {\i1}my{\i0} training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:25.31,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put yourself and ordinary people at the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.34,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much to eat on that island; they'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.21,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How do we eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... We cut it apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:41.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I did the catching; you do the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You always try to make me do all the things you don't want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.50,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Baby foxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forget meat... let's try for some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.62,0:12:27.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How do we catch one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:30.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a rod, line, or a needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:43.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No food, no fire, no nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:45.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:52.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Eating ants and living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Eating life and living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:07.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Living...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost there, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.85,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like tomorrow's the end of the month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:09.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,did you ever find the answer to "One is All, All is One"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:16.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it for the longest time, but I only kind of understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:19.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not positive, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:23.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I ate ants when we were starving and out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:27.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They were so sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a thought came to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't eaten them and eventually died,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,foxes and ants would eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:39.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'd return to the soil and become grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:41.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what a rabbit would eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The food chain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:50.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Even this island could have been underwater in the ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:54.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And tens of thousands of years in the future,\Nit could be a summit of a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:01.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is within a large stream that can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:06.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that stream should be called the universe or the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:11.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but from the point of view of something that big, you and I are like ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A small individual within a stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're just "one" within the "all".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:24.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But only when those "ones" gather together, can an "all" exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.17,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the promised day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear your answer to "One is All, All is One".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"All" is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And "One" is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:46.15,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We can start the real training now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.11,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:55.24,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,A basis of a transmutation circle is the power of the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.01,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The circle displays the circulation of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:03.04,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and by sketching the construction symbol in it,\Nit becomes possible to activate its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.34,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is also a circulation of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.82,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to experience it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.44,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:26.28,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Review it until lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The circle displays the circulation of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:38.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,and by sketching the construction symbol in it,\Nit becomes possible to activate its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But you were transmuting by just slapping your palms together, weren't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not need to sketch the construction symbols?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.67,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I am like a construction symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to do in order to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.60,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to do it if you ever reach the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:10.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Master has also seen the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:22.89,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And? What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:24.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:41.68,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you can transmute without a construction symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.93,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, Alphonse is an empty suit of armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.46,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You've got automails for an arm and leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.46,0:18:50.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell from just sparring with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You... saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:18:59.74,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:06.62,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Both master and pupil, making the same stupid decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because you saw that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:03.47,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We had a hard time conceiving a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:09.18,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just when we thought we were having a baby, I fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:15.76,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, our child wasn't born into this world alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:17.86,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,...I committed taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.95,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, all sorts of organs were taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.60,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:36.03,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:44.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's something we did to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We don't particularly find it tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:51.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I think about what to eat when I get my body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite the opposite; it's more of an anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:57.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.98,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You morons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.65,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No need to force yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:26.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:28.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:42.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This world is flowing while abiding by a great rule that's unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:46.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Learning about that flow,\Nbreaking it down, and rebuilding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's what alchemy's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:52.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also what living is about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:57.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The basics of alchemy, breaking\Nsomething down and rebuilding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:59.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost like the food chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:05.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat a rabbit, you break down\Nits meat and rebuild it into your own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:10.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And even that rabbit rebuilds\Nthe grass it ate into its own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:14.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.21,0:24:00.83,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A man who enjoys his own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:03.12,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:11.01,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he be friend or foe, the figure that stands before Ed and Al is a body made for fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.79,0:24:16.29,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:20.27,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13, The Beasts of Dublith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:25.06,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful figure appears before the two.
